2008-10-27  OpenUSB Community  <libusb-devel@lists.sourceforge.net>

	* Version updated from 1.0.1 to 1.0.2
	* Added preliminary darwin backend supporting
	* Fixed bugs in USB io transfers
	* Changed LIBUSB_* to OPENUSB_*
	* Enhanced multi-thread supporting
	* Fixed bugs in setting and getting device's configuration
	* Changed malloc() to calloc() to get zero'ed memory
	* Fixed device discovery on multiporcess systems
	* Fixed bugs in lock and unlock

2008-02-22  OpenUSB Community <libusb-devel@lists.sourceforge.net>

	* Version 1.0.1 was released to fix minor issues of OpenUSB version 1.0

2007-12-21  OpenUSB Community <libusb-devel@lists.sourceforge.net>

	* Initial implementation of OpenUSB interfaces, with Solaris and Linux
	  backend support
	* Supported mulit-thread safe
	* Supported isochronous transfer
	* See more information on http://openusb.sourceforge.net/
